Notes: SP's Boehning becomes 10th player in SP history to score 1,000th career point
...SP's Kraemer's 20 points are a career high...SP jumped out to 11-2 lead and
Carroll cut lead to 28-24 before SP pushed lead back up to 13 points...Carroll
cut lead to five points in final minute...SP has not trailed this season.
Game.Officials: David Delsman,  Rodney Harrington,  Dorran Stewart
